                   README File for simpleDemo Example 

The simpleDemo example demonstrates how to instantiate the ExmSimple
demonstration widget in a C application. To build the program, just type 

 $ make

To run the program, just type:

 $ simpleDemo

For an explanation of how this program works, see Chapter 2 of the 
"OSF/Motif Widget Writer's Guide." 
